      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 12:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国法官裁定伦敦资本与金融公司老板实施庞氏骗局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/london-capital-finance-bosses-ran-a-ponzi-scheme-uk-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦一名法官裁定，伦敦资本与金融有限公司 (London Capital &amp; Finance Plc) 的老板实施庞氏骗局，从散户投资者手中收取数亿英镑，并将其中大部分花在自己身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/london-capital-finance-bosses-ran-a-ponzi-scheme-uk-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库格勒称美联储必须同时关注通胀和就业目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kugler-says-fed-must-focus-on-both-inflation-and-jobs-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事阿德里安娜·库格勒表示，政策制定者必须同时关注央行的通胀和就业目标，并指出劳动力市场正在降温，实现美联储 2% 通胀目标的进展放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kugler-says-fed-must-focus-on-both-inflation-and-jobs-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
